** My translation
Aah, in a trance, in space, I think I'll have an amazing love
Inside a book, going to that library, riding a white bicycle.

Wearing a black tie, in the London wind, and a quickly chosen miniskirt
Anyway, my heart dances, what kind of story will today be?
Whether it's a 40 degree midsummer's day or a Siberian blizzard,,
it doesn't matter to me, I'll be hurrying to the library. 

NO NO NO You don't understand anything!
Inside books is a spectcular rainbow!

Aah, in a trance, in space, I think I'll have an amazing love inside a book
Turning the pages, I once again fall into a NEW love!
Is it life, this feeling? Is it fresh passion, this feeling?
So I'm going there right now.

My hair is swaying, going sara sara, the wind's touch is going fuwa fuwa
This moment, like the moment of being kissed, is good.
Every day, I never have enough, Papa and Mama, don't worry
Going into a trance is the greatest felicity.

Yeah yeah yeah, it's the for you, isn't it?
Something has to send you into a trance, or else it's no good, isn't it?
Super entertainment!

It's not here, wherever it is in this world, I think I love that place. Come on, hurry!
Hey, quickly, flip to the next page, my heart is beating, don't be impatient
In a real trance, in space, I think I'll have an amazing love.
In a book, going to that library on a white bicycle!
Ah! Drinking cider! Ah! Blowing a whistle! Ah! Looking up at the blue sky!

But sometime, true love,
don't you want to try it out? True love.
Sometime, true love,
can I do it with you?

